         <div xml:id="alalal-f24454"><!-- l3d35dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-f24454-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f24454-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="20"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
<lb ed="Bd" n="21"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-f24454-Qd1e109"> Post premissa diligenter 
consideran<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="22"/>dum, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f24454-d1e115">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="23"/>In hac parte agit de differentia 
dono<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="24"/>rum, quae sunt in anima secundum 
intel<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="25"/>lectum. Et versatur intentio istius 
distin<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="26"/>clionis circa quinque: in quorum primo
<lb ed="Bd" n="27"/>distinguit inter sapientiam et scientiam. 
<lb ed="Bd" n="28"/>In secundo, inter sapientiam et 
intelle<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="29"/>ctum, ibi, B,ยง 1: <quote xml:id="alalal-f24454-Qd1e132"> Ostensa differentia,
<lb ed="Bd" n="30"/>etc. </quote> In tertio, distinguit similiter inter
<lb ed="Bd" n="31"/>sapientiam et scientiam et intellectum,
<lb ed="Bd" n="32"/>ibi, B, ยง 2: <quote xml:id="alalal-f24454-Qd1e141"> Sie ergo distingui potest, 
<lb ed="Bd" n="33"/>etc. </quote> In quarto, distinguit inter sapien-
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f24454-d1e147">
               <cb ed="#Bd" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="34"/>tiam et scientiam et intellectum ut dona,
<lb ed="Bd" n="35"/>et eadem secundum quod sunt habitus
<lb ed="Bd" n="36"/>acquisiti per studium et non dona, 
se<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="37"/>cundum quod hic accipiuntur dona, ibi,
<lb ed="Bd" n="38"/>C, <quote xml:id="alalal-f24454-Qd1e162"> Et notandum, etc. </quote> Quinto et 
ulti<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="39"/>mo, inter sapientiam donum Dei, et 
sa<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="40"/>pientiam divinam, ibi, D, <quote xml:id="alalal-f24454-Qd1e168"> Illud etiam
<lb ed="Bd" n="41"/>sciendum, etc. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
